    "Every raw topic in the DB must map to exactly one canonical parent",
    "If a raw topic is not listed, it falls through to 'unmapped' and is excluded from hub pages",
    "canonical_slug becomes the URL: /free-{subject}-worksheets/grade-{N}/{canonical_slug}/",
